Crafting effective error messages involves ensuring clarity, specificity, and user-centeredness.
Anthropomorphic guidelines advise against presenting computers as people, advocating for comprehensible, predictable, and controllable interfaces.
In display design, utilize visual displays effectively to showcase data trends, relationships, and comparisons, ensuring appropriateness for the data presented.
